## Features
- Fetches movie data from the OMDb API
- Displays movies in a grid layout with individual movie cards
- Search bar for finding movies by title or keyword
- Filter by movie type (movie, series, episode)
- View detailed movie information, including plot, cast, and ratings
- Add and remove favorite movies (persisted in localStorage)
- Pagination for browsing large result sets
- Responsive design for optimal viewing on all devices

